<section class="skills" id="skills">
  <div class="container">
    <h2 class="section-title">// Skills & Profile</h2>
    
    <div class="profile-grid">
      <div class="profile-card">
        <h3>$ whoami</h3>
        <p>Técnico en sistemas con habilidades en creación, reparación y mantenimiento de hardware y software. Experiencia práctica en desarrollo web y configuración de equipos de red (switches/routers) mediante SSH. Habilidades blandas desarrolladas como monitor académico.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="profile-card">
        <h3>$ cat objective.txt</h3>
        <p>Desarrollar, mantener y dar soporte de software, red de internet o hardware para una empresa o cliente.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="skills-grid">
      <div class="skill-category">
        <h3>Web Development</h3>
        <p class="skill-tags">> React > JavaScript > CSS > HTML</p>
      </div>

      <div class="skill-category">
        <h3>Programming</h3>
        <p class="skill-tags">> Java > Python</p>
      </div>

      <div class="skill-category">
        <h3>Networking</h3>
        <p class="skill-tags">> Cisco (L2/L3) > IPv4/IPv6 > VLAN > DHCP > NAT</p>
      </div>

      <div class="skill-category">
        <h3>Systems & Tools</h3>
        <p class="skill-tags">> Linux > Windows > VirtualBox > Figma > Packet Tracer</p>
      </div>

      <div class="skill-category">
        <h3>Security</h3>
        <p class="skill-tags">> Firewalls > Vulnerability Analysis > Best Practices</p>
      </div>

      <div class="skill-category">
        <h3>Hardware</h3>
        <p class="skill-tags">> Assembly > Repair > Diagnostics</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .skills {
    min-height: 100vh;
    padding: 4rem 2rem;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .container {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .profile-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .profile-card {
    background: rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-matrix-primary);
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }

  .profile-card:hover {
    background: rgba(0, 55, 20, 0.1);
    box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(57, 255, 20, 0.2);
    transform: translateY(-4px);
  }

  .profile-card h3 {
    font-family: var(--font-matrix);
    color: var(--color-matrix-primary);
    margin: 0 0 1rem 0;
    font-size: 1.2rem;
  }

  .profile-card p {
    color: #ddd;
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .skills-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .skill-category {
    background: rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-matrix-primary);
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }

  .skill-category:hover {
    background: rgba(0, 55, 20, 0.1);
    box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(57, 255, 20, 0.2);
    transform: translateY(-4px);
  }

  .skill-category h3 {
    font-family: var(--font-matrix);
    color: var(--color-matrix-primary);
    margin: 0 0 1rem 0;
    font-size: 1.2rem;
  }

  .skill-tags {
    font-family: var(--font-terminal);
    color: #ddd;
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin: 0;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .skills {
      padding: 3rem 1rem;
    }
  }

  .section-title {
    font-family: var(--font-matrix);
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3rem);
    color: var(--color-matrix-primary);
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
    text-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(57, 255, 20, 0.5);
  }
</style>